nodes.text: The New Jedi Order: Vector Prime (audiobook)

The New Jedi Order: Vector Prime is the abridged audio version of the Legends novel of the same name, by author R. A. Salvatore. The audiobook was performed by Anthony Heald and was released by Bantam Doubleday Dell Audio Publishing on October 5, 1999. It was later digitally released by Random House Audio on February 20, 2007.
